OL,3,CEx-Scotland rugby captain Stuart Hogg
OL,4,Ccomplies with court order
OL,6,FFormer Scotland rugby captain Stuart
OL,7,FHogg is "fully complying" with a
OL,8,Fsupervision order imposed after he
OL,9,Fadmitted to abusing his estranged wife
OL,10,Fover five years, a court has heard.
OL,12,FThe 32-year-old pleaded guilty to a
OL,13,Fsingle charge of domestic abuse of his
OL,14,Fex-partner, Gillian Hogg, when he
OL,15,Fappeared at Selkirk Sheriff Court in
OL,16,FNovember last year.
OL,18,FHe admitted shouting and swearing,
OL,19,Ftracking her movements and sending her
OL,20,Fmessages which were alarming and
OL,21,Fdistressing in nature.
