OL,3,CEx-Scotland rugby captain Stuart Hogg
OL,4,Ccomplies with court order
OL,6,FSheriff Peter Paterson sentenced Hogg
OL,7,Fto a community payback order with one
OL,8,Fyear of supervision as an alternative
OL,9,Fto jail when he sentenced him in
OL,10,FJanuary 2025. He was also banned him
OL,11,Ffrom approaching or contacting Mrs
OL,12,FHogg for five years.
OL,14,FA review of his order took place at
OL,15,FJedburgh Sheriff Court on Tuesday,
OL,16,Fwhich Hogg was excused from attending.
OL,18,FHis lawyer Mat Patrick told the court
OL,19,FHogg is "fully complying" with his
OL,20,Fsupervision order.
