OL,3,CEx-Scotland rugby captain Stuart Hogg
OL,4,Ccomplies with court order
OL,6,FHe said: "We are just shy of three
OL,7,Fmonths into the order and the review
OL,8,Freport confirms that he is fully
OL,9,Fcomplying with the appointments, there
OL,10,Fhave been no missed appointments.
OL,12,F"As far as progress is concerned, it
OL,13,Flooks like progress requires to be
OL,14,Fmade but it is a 12-month order and is
OL,15,Fagainst the background of quite a
OL,16,Fdifficult divorce which is ongoing at
OL,17,Fthe moment and all the emotions that
OL,18,Fcan come with that, and that has
OL,19,Fplayed a part.
OL,21,F"Obviously there is work to be done."
