OL,3,CEx-Scotland rugby captain Stuart Hogg
OL,4,Ccomplies with court order
OL,6,FSheriff Paterson said it is "not
OL,7,Fentirely surprising" that Hogg might
OL,8,Ffeel "hard done by", but he needs to
OL,9,Fmove on.
OL,11,FHe said: "He is the one that pleaded
OL,12,Fguilty and he has to face the
OL,13,Fconsequences of his actions and he has
OL,14,Fto move on from that."
OL,16,FThe sheriff has fixed a further review
OL,17,Fof the order to take place 16 June
OL,18,F2025.
