OL,3,CEx-Scotland rugby captain Stuart Hogg
OL,4,Ccomplies with court order
OL,6,FHe added: "If progress is satisfactory
OL,7,Fhe will not have to attend, but if
OL,8,Fthere is any difficulty he will have
OL,9,Fto attend."
OL,11,FThe former Glasgow Warriors fullback
OL,12,Famassed a century of senior caps for
OL,13,Fhis country and was involved in three
OL,14,FBritish and Irish Lions tours.
OL,16,FHe remains one of Scotland's all-time
OL,17,Fleading try scorers and was awarded an
OL,18,FMBE in the 2024 New Year honours list
OL,19,Ffor services to rugby union.
